snippet.title: New Concept Trailer: Into the Deep - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
"I shall step into the city of sorrows, and I shall fall into eternal torment."
Please leave, lost traveler.
The threads tangled between us, I still don't want to... have them severed now.
Voice Cast: Griseo - 木野日菜
Pardofelis - 山本希望
Kosma - 小林千晃
Vill-V - 金元寿子
Aponia - 白石晴香
